00:33:10.150 --> 00:33:12.190
TOM BROXTON: Yeah, OK.

00:33:12.190 --> 00:33:19.210
I think a lot of our initial
impulse is driven out of the

00:33:19.210 --> 00:33:21.000
frustration we see
with search.

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:26.410
So if you look at our TV
