00:33:49.240 --> 00:33:52.126
together off a common service.

00:33:52.126 --> 00:33:55.720
So rather than trying to build
specific remote control apps,

00:33:55.720 --> 00:33:58.650
as we'd seen other people do, we
were trying to think about

00:33:58.650 --> 00:34:02.080
well, I really should be able
to search for my content

00:34:02.080 --> 00:34:03.430
anywhere and play it anywhere.

00:34:03.430 --> 00:34:07.690
So that was one of the
underlying principles of the

00:34:07.690 --> 00:34:08.889
UI we were trying to develop.

00:34:08.889 --> 00:34:12.260
And not develop new apps, but
think about, OK, we've already

00:34:12.260 --> 00:34:13.179
got a mobile phone app.

00:34:13.179 --> 00:34:14.670
And we've already
got a TV app.

00:34:14.670 --> 00:34:17.469
What's the best way of
connecting these two together,

00:34:17.469 --> 00:34:21.320
