00:36:08.710 --> 00:36:09.920
How does it start on the TV?

00:36:09.920 --> 00:36:12.410
And we're really starting to
think about desktop as an

00:36:12.410 --> 00:36:15.230
equal instead of the first
thing we think about.

00:36:15.230 --> 00:36:18.600
And so it's actually a pretty
